"" "" "" "never before in my life someone wrote me something so beautiful, so I answer it." "" "suddenly the tears run over the cheeks." ""
I hugged him very tightly and sat down beside the pomegranates.
Perhaps he was tired of the war, was sorry to be the faithful companion of this struggle all the years, and wanted to help him write this letter.
